com.androidex.logger

类 MessageOnlyLogFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.androidex.logger.MessageOnlyLogFilter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    LogNode

    public class MessageOnlyLogFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements LogNode
    Simple LogNode filter, removes everything except the message. Useful for situations like on-screen log output where you don't want a lot of metadata displayed, just easy-to-read message updates as they're happening.
